data.name: addressCustomersResult.Scripts.OnBeforePrint
data.value:
Private Sub OnBeforePrint(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.Drawing.Printing.PrintEventArgs) Dim result as XRLabel = sender Dim _StrEntryStreetAddress as string = GetCurrentColumnValue("entry_street_address").ToString()
result.Text = addressCustomers.Text.Replace("$$$addressCustomers$$$" , Microsoft.VisualBasic.StrConv(_StrEntryStreetAddress, Microsoft.VisualBasic.VbStrConv.ProperCase) )
result.text = System.Text.Encoding.ASCII.GetString(System.Text.Encoding.GetEncoding(1251).GetBytes(result.text))
End Sub
